highEngagement.author: mert
highEngagement.text:
this is a false equivalence

a DEX does not "list" all tokens, it is [in theory] a non-custodial permissionless backend and it's the job of frontends to curate

on the contrary, a CEX literally custodies the tokens and is thus responsible for them
